===''Pokémon the Series''===
{{main|Professor Kukui (anime)}}
Professor Kukui is a regular character in {{aniseries|SM}}, who debuted in ''[[SM001|Alola to New Adventure!]]''. He works as a teacher at the [[Pokémon School]] of [[Melemele Island]]. {{Ash}} lived with him while attending the school as one of his students. Much like the games, Kukui uses the alias "the Masked Royal" whenever he competes at the [[Battle Royal]], and is married to {{an|Professor Burnet}}. He reappears in {{aniseries|JN}}, where he and Burnet now have a son named [[Lei]].
